      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must be verified under an FDA-recognized SQA plan with documented version control, regression testing, and audit trail for all simulation runs submitted in the regulatory package.",
      "rationale": "SQA documentation covers version control and basic regression tests but lacks a formal FDA-recognized SQA plan and full audit trail. Achieved level 2 falls short of required level 4 at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
