      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry, flow regime, and blood analogue must match the VAD COU within documented similarity bounds; any departures must be justified by formal similarity analysis.",
      "rationale": "Validation was conducted on the FDA generic pump geometry rather than the actual VAD geometry. No formal similarity analysis was provided to justify geometric extrapolation. Achieved level 2 is far below required level 5."
    },
