      "acceptanceCriteria": "A formal parameter equivalency analysis must demonstrate that validation experiment input conditions are equivalent (within defined bounds) to the COU operating conditions for all five flow-speed combinations.",
      "rationale": "No parameter equivalency analysis was performed between validation experiment conditions and VAD COU operating conditions. The gap is particularly significant for rotational speed and haematocrit levels. Flagged as epistemic gap; achieved level 1."
